If youd like a value set with the sysctl command to take effect on boot, within whichfile should you place the variable and its value?
A)  /etc/sysctl.cfg
B)  /etc/sysctl.conf
C)  /lib/sysctl
D)  /var/sysctl.conf
B
B. Variables and values placed in /etc/sysctl.conf will take effect on boot. The otherfiles listed are not valid.
